# ===========================
# Aether Agents — .gitignore
# ===========================

# --- Secrets (NEVER commit) ---
.env
*.env
!.env.example

# --- Runtime (auto-generated) ---
home/sessions/
home/logs/
home/plugins/
home/.cache/
**/sessions/
**/request_dump*
**/logs/

# --- Auth and model caches ---
**/auth.json
**/models_dev_cache.json

# --- Hermes runtime files ---
**/state.db
**/auth.lock
**/.skills_prompt_snapshot.json
**/.hermes_history
**/checkpoints/
home/skills/.hub/

# --- Profile skills directories (skills loaded via external_dirs from home/skills/) ---
home/profiles/*/skills/*
!home/profiles/*/skills/.gitkeep

# --- Per-profile bundled manifests (auto-generated) ---
**/.bundled_manifest

# --- Hermes auto-generated configs ---
home/config.yaml
home/profiles/hermes/config.yaml

# --- Hermes runtime dirs ---
home/profiles/hermes/bin/
home/profiles/hermes/sandboxes/
home/profiles/hermes/cron/

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.eggs/
venv/
.venv/

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- IDE ---
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Prometeo (personal assistant — private) ---
home/profiles/prometeo/

# --- Project state (local only) ---
.eter/
**/.olympus_checkpoints.db*
**/state.db-shm
**/state.db-wal

# --- Claude Code (dev tool) ---
.claude/

# --- Development artifacts ---
PROMPT_OPUS.md
CLAUDE.md
docs/sesiones/
docs/setup/
